1
00:00:02,840 --> 00:00:04,120
You finally
came out for once.

2
00:00:04,120 --> 00:00:05,840
Cheer up.

3
00:00:06,720 --> 00:00:08,480
I'm here because the Krits
sent me on an errand.

4
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:10,680
Why did they ask you
to bring me here?

5
00:00:10,920 --> 00:00:13,160
The Phisit family
came to Burin again.

6
00:00:13,400 --> 00:00:15,680
The governor hired them
for security,

7
00:00:15,680 --> 00:00:18,400
but they
haven't agreed yet.

8
00:00:18,600 --> 00:00:21,680
They sent the second son,
Mr. Napat,

9
00:00:22,160 --> 00:00:23,120
to Burin

10
00:00:23,640 --> 00:00:24,560
to inspect the governor.

11
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:27,000
What does that
have to do with me?

12
00:00:27,840 --> 00:00:31,080
The governor heard
Mr. Napat likes fencing,

13
00:00:31,680 --> 00:00:34,280
so he's looking for
someone to spar with him.

14
00:00:34,600 --> 00:00:36,800
Is the Phisit family
powerful?

15
00:00:37,400 --> 00:00:40,480
They're a major mafia
in Asia.

16
00:00:40,840 --> 00:00:42,360
They're brutal.

17
00:00:43,120 --> 00:00:45,200
I need to find a way
to help you.

18
00:00:45,480 --> 00:00:47,400
If he asks, just say
you don't want to.

19
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:52,080
I don't think
I can avoid it.

20
00:00:53,280 --> 00:00:53,920
Let's go inside.

21
00:00:59,280 --> 00:00:59,880
Stop.

22
00:01:03,760 --> 00:01:05,880
Mr. Napat, are you
trying to get me killed?

23
00:01:10,080 --> 00:01:11,160
I'm sorry,

24
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:13,800
but I really can't find
any info on that waiter.

25
00:01:14,440 --> 00:01:15,520
Who's he?

26
00:01:15,520 --> 00:01:17,840
Why are you
so concerned?

27
00:01:19,160 --> 00:01:21,440
Stop asking.
Just find him.

28
00:01:22,720 --> 00:01:23,680
I'm going to the sauna.

29
00:01:25,080 --> 00:01:26,000
You're leaving me here?

30
00:01:34,720 --> 00:01:36,840
I don't think you have
much talent for fencing.

31
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:38,960
Why insist on training?

32
00:01:39,840 --> 00:01:40,480
Well,

33
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:42,080
there's a sauna here.

34
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:44,240
Go take a steam.

35
00:01:48,720 --> 00:01:49,240
Thanks.
